OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1779477072
OL,3,CCinema bans under-16s without parents
OL,4,Cafter 7pm
OL,6,FA Welsh cinema has banned under-16s
OL,7,Ffrom watching films without their
OL,8,Fparents in the evening after issues
OL,9,Fwith anti-social behaviour.
OL,11,FThe cinema said all children under the
OL,12,Fage of 16 must now be accompanied at
OL,13,Fscreenings from 7pm by a responsible
OL,14,Fadult in order to tackle the issue.
OL,16,FGaleri, a cinema and arts centre in
OL,17,FCaernarfon in north Wales, said it has
OL,18,Freceived "an increasing number of
OL,19,Fcomplaints about anti-social behaviour
OL,20,Ffrom some young people in our cinema
OL,21,Fscreens".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
