FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1779477072
OL,3,CCinema bans under-16s without parents
OL,4,Cafter 7pm
OL,6,FIt said incidents included damaging
OL,7,Fseats, shouting at customers, filming
OL,8,Fin the screens and acting in a
OL,9,F"disruptive manner", adding that they
OL,10,Fwere temporarily changing their
OL,11,Faudience policies "with a heavy heart."
OL,13,FThe cinema said if a responsible adult
OL,14,Fis not present, or if age cannot be
OL,15,Fverified, entry will not be allowed.
OL,17,F"We sincerely apologise for this and
OL,18,Fgreatly appreciate your
OL,19,Funderstanding," Galeri wrote in a
OL,20,Fstatement posted online.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/3
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
