PN,46603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1779477072
OL,3,CCinema bans under-16s without parents
OL,4,Cafter 7pm
OL,6,F"We would like to emphasise that this
OL,7,Fis a temporary arrangement, and we
OL,8,Fwill be closely monitoring the
OL,9,Fsituation as we work towards a longer-
OL,10,Fterm solution. Please help us to
OL,11,Frespect this valuable community asset
OL,12,Fand look after it."
